    "name": "我们把似曾相见的「那些游戏」都做成了火柴人，可是你又能否成功过关呢？",
    "steam_appid": 2348100,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348100/extras/17455f2204de8cae9a8b1119572daf3f.poster.avif?t=1704939030\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348100/extras/17455f2204de8cae9a8b1119572daf3f.webm?t=1704939030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348100/extras/17455f2204de8cae9a8b1119572daf3f.mp4?t=1704939030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>“那些游戏”，<br>是将大家曾经产生过玩一玩念想的那些游戏，以既滑稽又可爱的火柴人作为角色，制作而成的能够足足、慢慢、尽情游玩的小游戏合集。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348100/extras/13527667f0a994a680c64ac68fb33e4f.poster.avif?t=1704939030\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348100/extras/13527667f0a994a680c64ac68fb33e4f.webm?t=1704939030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348100/extras/13527667f0a994a680c64ac68fb33e4f.mp4?t=1704939030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在“游玩小游戏”中通关各种小游戏的关卡以及完成任务吧！<br>通关各个小游戏内的所有关卡后，<br>就会解锁对应小游戏的“挑战排名”！<br>可在当月排名中，与地区内所有玩家比拼通关时间或分数！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348100/extras/722591c08ff39b64a7b989731a6a6183.poster.avif?t=1704939030\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348100/extras/722591c08ff39b64a7b989731a6a6183.webm?t=1704939030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348100/extras/722591c08ff39b64a7b989731a6a6183.mp4?t=1704939030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>使用游戏内获得的硬币抽取扭蛋吧！<br>获得名牌或称号后，就自定义在自己专属的名牌上吧！<br>名牌与称号的组合搭配将会达到惊人的8,910,000种！<br>帅气的组合是不错，不过也去发现一些令人不禁发笑的组合吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348100/extras/cdb2cc3355d46fe73f1802066a68b6de.poster.avif?t=1704939030\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348100/extras/cdb2cc3355d46fe73f1802066a68b6de.webm?t=1704939030\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2348100/extras/cdb2cc3355d46fe73f1802066a68b6de.mp4?t=1704939030\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>主要功能<br>·把似曾相见的“那些游戏”以火柴人形象做成了游戏！<br>·以3D形式表现出的既滑稽又可爱的形象与动作！<br>·能够尽情享受“那些游戏”的“游玩小游戏”<br>·与地区内所有玩家比拼“那些游戏”的“挑战排名”<br>·使用硬币获得名牌与称号的“扭蛋”<br>·使用名牌与称号制作自己专属名牌的“自定义名牌”<br>·能够查看地区内所有玩家当月排名的“最新排名”<br>·完成各种任务条件获得报酬的“任务”功能也丰富多彩！",
